SAPS4D.MA07V


SELECT T1."MANDT", T1."MATNR", T2."WERKS", T1."MTART", T1."MBRSH", T1."MATKL", T1."MEINS",T1."BRGEW", T1."GEWEI",
       T1."VOLUM", T1."DISST", T1."WESCH", T1."ETIFO",T1."ETIAR", T2."PSTAT", T2."LVORM", T2."BWTTY", T2."XCHAR",
       T2."AUSME", T2."XCHPF",T2."DISMM", T2."DISPO", T2."PLIFZ", T2."WEBAZ", T2."EISBE", T2."MINBE", T2."BESKZ",
       T2."SOBSL", T2."PERKZ", T2."SSQSS", T2."UMLMC", T2."TRAME", T2."PERIV",T1."SPART", T2."MMSTA", T2."MMSTD",
       T2."MISKZ", T2."WZEIT", T2."VRMOD", T2."VINT1",T2."VINT2", T2."MTVFP", T2."DISGR", T2."APOKZ", T2."ABCIN",
       T2."PRCTR", T2."XMCNG",T2."SERNP", T1."EKWSL", T1."MHDRZ", T1."MHDHB", T1."MHDLP", T2."CCFIX",T2."EPRIO",
       T2."DZEIT", T1."PRDHA", T1."SATNR", T1."PLGTP", T1."SAISO", T1."BWVOR",T1."BWSCL", T1."VOLEH", T2."SERVG",
       T2."STRGR", T2."PRFRQ", T2."STDPD", T2."CUOBJ",T1."MLGUT", T2."QMATV", T1."SAISJ", T2."VKUMC", T2."VKTRW",
       T1."ATTYP",T1."CUOBF", T1."SERLV", T2."GLGMG", T2."VKGLG", T1."KZWSM", T1."IPRKZ", T1."RDMHD",T2."MCRUE",
       T2."LADGR", T1."BFLME", T2."DIBER", T2."UCHKZ", T2."BWESB", T2."SGT_COVS",T2."SGT_STATC", T2."SGT_SCOPE",
       T1."/CWM/XCWMAT", T1."/CWM/VALUM",T1."/CWM/TOLGR", T1."FSH_SEALV", T1."FSH_SEAIM", T1."XGRDT"
FROM "MARA" T1, "MARC"T2
WHERE T1."MANDT" = T2."MANDT"
  AND T1."MATNR" = T2."MATNR"

SAPS4D.V_MMIM_OM_BYPO


SELECT DISTINCT "MATDOC"."MANDT" AS "MANDT", "MATDOC"."MBLNR", "MATDOC"."MJAHR","MATDOC"."EBELN", "EKKO"."WEAKT",
                MIN("MATDOC"."ZEILE") AS "ZEILE"
FROM "MATDOC""MATDOC"
INNER JOIN "EKKO" "EKKO" ON ("MATDOC"."MANDT" = "EKKO"."MANDT"
                             AND"EKKO"."EBELN" = "MATDOC"."EBELN")
WHERE "MATDOC"."RECORD_TYPE" = N'MDOC' GROUPBY "MATDOC"."MANDT", "MATDOC"."EBELN", "MATDOC"."MBLNR", "MATDOC"."MJAHR",
                                       "EKKO"."WEAKT"

SAPS4D.V_MMIM_OM_PARAM


SELECT "DOCUMENT"."MANDT" AS "SAPCLIENT",
       CONCAT(RTRIM ("DOCUMENT"."MBLNR") ,RTRIM (CONCAT(RTRIM ("DOCUMENT"."MJAHR") , RTRIM ("DOCUMENT"."ZEILE")))) AS "MATDOCKEY", "DOCUMENT"."MBLNR" AS "MATERIALDOCUMENT", "DOCUMENT"."MJAHR"AS "MATERIALDOCUMENTYEAR",
       "DOCUMENT"."ZEILE" AS "MATERIALDOCUMENTITEM", "DOCUMENT"."EBELN"AS "PURCHASINGDOCUMENT", "DOCUMENT"."VGART" AS "INVENTORYTRANSACTIONTYPE",
       "DOCUMENT"."WEVER" AS "VERSIONFORPRINTINGSLIP", "DOCUMENT"."USNAM" AS "CREATIONUSERNAME","DOCUMENT"."SHKZG" AS "QUANTITYDEBITCREDITCODE",
       "PRINTIND"."KZWES"AS "GOODSRECEIPTISMOVEDTOBLKDSTOCK", "DOCUMENT"."WERKS" AS "PLANT", "DOCUMENT"."LGORT"AS "STORAGELOCATION",
       "DOCUMENT"."BWART" AS "GOODSMOVEMENTTYPE", "DOCUMENT"."WEANZ"AS "NMBROFGRORGISLIPSTOPRINTQTY",
       "DOCUMENT"."BUDAT" AS "MATLDOCLATESTPOSTGDATE","PRINTIND"."KZDRU" AS "PRINTINGOFDOCUMENTITEM", "PRINTPO"."WEAKT"AS "INDGOODSRECEIPTMESSAGE",
       "DOCUMENT"."XPRINT" AS "OPERATIONISPRINTED", "DOCUMENT"."BUKRS"AS "COMPANYCODE", "DOCUMENT"."LIFNR" AS "SUPPLIER",
       "=A0"."ETIFO"AS "LABELFORM", "=A0"."ETIAR" AS "LABELTYPE"
FROM ((("MATDOC" "DOCUMENT" INNERJOIN "T156" "PRINTIND" ON ("DOCUMENT"."MANDT" = "PRINTIND"."MANDT"
                                                            AND "DOCUMENT"."BWART"= "PRINTIND"."BWART"))
       LEFT OUTER JOIN "EKKO" "PURCHORD" ON ("DOCUMENT"."MANDT" = "PURCHORD"."MANDT"
                                             AND "DOCUMENT"."EBELN" = "PURCHORD"."EBELN"))
      LEFT OUTER JOIN "V_MMIM_OM_BYPO" "PRINTPO" ON ("PRINTPO"."MBLNR" = "DOCUMENT"."MBLNR"
                                                     AND "PRINTPO"."MJAHR" = "DOCUMENT"."MJAHR"
                                                     AND "PRINTPO"."ZEILE"= "DOCUMENT"."ZEILE"
                                                     AND "DOCUMENT"."MANDT" = "PRINTPO"."MANDT")) LEFT OUTER MANYTO ONE
JOIN "MA07V" "=A0" ON ("DOCUMENT"."MATNR" = "=A0"."MATNR"
                       AND "DOCUMENT"."WERKS"= "=A0"."WERKS"
                       AND "DOCUMENT"."MANDT" = "=A0"."MANDT")
WHERE "DOCUMENT"."RECORD_TYPE"= N'MDOC'
